### Register
POST http://{{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://{{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Me
GET http://{{host}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
